        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "## Cognitive tasks that are binary processes\n",
        "::: incremental\n",
        "- Task switching\n",
        "- Go-no-go\n",
        "- Stop signal\n",
        "- etc. \n",
        ":::\n",
